{"tid":388390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯:建議巴士延誤罰則機制，對巴士脫班或延誤作出罰款","createTime":"2017-09-05T12:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T13:19:11.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37cedb7171354ec13d4851dc9675a59024e3659c","tid":388390,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"悠長暑假完結後，莘莘學子在早上起床後又要「迫巴士」趕上學。有政黨於今(4日)早進行調查，發現早上7至9時的上學繁忙時間，在沙田不同地區監察37條巴士路線服務中，有約92%路線未能按照巴士公司的班次服務承諾提供服務，平均延誤比率達27.6%。 <br />\n<br />\n民建聯沙田支部進行的調查顯示，受查的37條巴士路線當中，有34條出現「脫班」情況，只有3條班次較少的路線能夠準時提供原定的班次服務。針對巴士脫班情況，建議運輸署設立冒士路線電子監察系統，並要求巴士公司公開數據，即時掌握全面巴士運作情況；及參考港鐵引入巴士延誤罰則機制，對巴士脫班或延誤超過一段時間作出罰款。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/mobile/bkn-20170904170635362-0904_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170904%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170904170635362-0904_00822_001.html&d=z0qExKJve019zTluS%2Ft0sy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8c8dacbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/mobile/bkn-20170904170635362-0904_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"47110a3788b1216c5ecf10a3fe25beac5c3a67a5","tid":388390,"uid":90766,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:16:35.000Z","msg":"唔塞車咪準時囉屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似屯門公路咁有邊日係唔撚塞架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫d私家車唔好係正繁忙時間先出嚟咪準時開到車囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9d42982e173a2fa75312a2b4d9788e2f6dfdb8","tid":388390,"uid":9707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"禮義廉竟然會做呢啲嘢？"},{"pid":"f56150795f317b349727f28e17360d40b28e8e09","tid":388390,"uid":10694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"車輛過多引致遲左 又入巴士數又唔太公平啵"},{"pid":"a98fca701b3dd89ccb6d9740858b5a1c20186d09","tid":388390,"uid":8040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:27:19.000Z","msg":"之後d 巴士變晒忙命巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又或者巴士公司set 到時間勁鬆，例如荃灣入屯門個半鐘，確保一定唔會遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d657b000167e7dced740c371412cdaf43d078927","tid":388390,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"到時早到左係咪會等夠鐘先開車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb14a6bbfeec02abc621b213d900a8e5000bd603","tid":388390,"uid":46431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母狗鐵條軌，個站，成個system都係私家野自己地盤<br />\n<br />\n但馬路就係公廁，個個都行得/用得<br />\n好老實巴士脫班，遲到多數都係因為塞車遲黎/或者無車返總站<br />\n<br />\n咁都有得用同一套標準黎衡量，禮義簾班假學歷西又再一次&quot;悔&quot;辱港燦智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心逗咁多錢一個月就用下個死人豬腦先出黎柒啦"},{"pid":"40b328fbe2d3fa50d3912a6a9e2653a21308f231","tid":388390,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:35:28.000Z","msg":"留名睇巴士佬屌鳩民建聯"},{"pid":"b2178180eca7720a6d7ebed2556f160d351cc370","tid":388390,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"好似想偏幫鐵路公司咁"},{"pid":"089589ea8b8b4a1c25807489a8c73f109632378b","tid":388390,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:36:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54daba025d124fb98d10c12234fb38e9c144e1be","tid":388390,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:36:26.000Z","msg":"民狗有冇爭取過巴士專綫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db70fdafe24f19fa6923c7d05f5c616d871316a9","tid":388390,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"人地地面有真塞車 on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c37e00a74a0d3305a1075e6021d0420741dc8d1","tid":388390,"uid":12277